IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EMPLOYEE-VALIDATION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 EMPLOYEE-NUMBER-STRING PIC X(5).
01 EMPLOYEE-NUMBER PIC 9(5).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 'ABCD' TO EMPLOYEE-NUMBER-STRING.
    IF EMPLOYEE-NUMBER-STRING NOT NUMERIC
        DISPLAY 'Invalid employee number: ' EMPLOYEE-NUMBER-STRING
    ELSE
        MOVE EMPLOYEE-NUMBER-STRING TO EMPLOYEE-NUMBER
        DISPLAY 'Valid employee number: ' EMPLOYEE-NUMBER
    END-IF.
    
    STOP RUN.